Name: Grilled salmon fish
Description: Tender, flavorful salmon fillet, grilled to perfection with secret herbs and spices.

Name: Fluffy Pancake Stack
Description: Indulgent pancakes, caramelized edges, topped with syrup, cream, and seasonal fruits.

Name: Juicy Sirloin Steak
Description: Prime beef, seared crust, juicy tenderness, served with roasted vegetables and savory sauces.

Name: Classic Beef Burger
Description: Beef patty, cheese, sesame seed bun, lettuce, tomato, onions, pickles, ketchup, mustard, and mayo.

Name: Chicken burger
Description: Grilled chicken breast, sesame seed bun, lettuce, tomato, onions, pickles, and choice of sauces.

Name: Fish sandwich
Description: Crispy fish fillet, soft bun, lettuce, tomato, tartar sauce.

Name: Pork roll
Description: Sliced and seasoned pork roll.

Name: Teriyaki chicken
Description: Chicken breast, teriyaki sauce (made with soy sauce, mirin, sugar, ginger, and garlic), and optional sesame seeds.

Name: Beef broccoli
Description: Beef strips, broccoli florets, soy sauce, garlic, ginger, and optional oyster sauce.

Name: Tempura sushi roll
Description: Sushi rice, nori (seaweed sheet), tempura-fried ingredients, soy sauce, and optional wasabi and pickled ginger.

Name: Spring roll

Name: Pad thai
Description: Rice noodles, tofu or choice of protein, eggs, bean sprouts, green onions, peanuts, tamarind sauce.

Name: Vegan pizza
Description: Vegan pizza dough, tomato sauce, vegan cheese, and assorted plant-based toppings.

Name: Ham cheese pizza
Description: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, ham slices.

Name: Chicken pizza
Description: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, grilled chicken, and choice of additional toppings.

Name: Pepperoni pizza
Description: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, pepperoni slices.

Name: Crispy fired chicken
Description: Chicken pieces, seasoned flour or batter, oil for frying.

Name: Onion rings
Description: Sliced onions, batter (made from flour, egg, milk, and seasoning), oil for frying.

Name: Chicken wings
Description: Chicken wings, choice of seasoning or sauce (e.g., buffalo, BBQ).

Name: Tempura vegetables
Description: Assorted vegetables (e.g., sweet potatoes, zucchini, bell peppers) coated in tempura batter and fried.

Name: Caesar salad
Description: Romaine lettuce, croutons, Parmesan cheese, Caesar dressing (made with anchovies, garlic, lemon juice, Dijon mustard, egg yolks, olive oil).

Name: Vegan wrap
Description: Wrap (e.g., tortilla), choice of vegan protein (e.g., tofu, chickpeas, tempeh), assorted vegetables, and vegan sauce or dressing.

Name: Coke
Description: Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine.

Name: Iced-tea
Description: Black tea or green tea, water, sugar or sweetener, lemon (optional).

Name: Lemonade
Description: Freshly squeezed lemons, water, sugar or sweetener.

Name: Coffee
Description: Coffee beans, hot water.

Name: Pappardelee pasta
Description: Wide and flat ribbons of egg-based pasta, made with flour and eggs.

Name: Linguine pasta
Description: Long, thin, and flat pasta similar to spaghetti, made with durum wheat semolina.

Name: fafalle pasta
Description: Bowtie-shaped pasta made with durum wheat semolina and water.
